comments.body:
@glasvandrare thanks for the problem report!  I'm assuming that in your example the $ubuntu_image variable was set to your image's id '0a85c244f0fb'.  I tried to replicate the issue using an image id like '0a85c244f0fb' and had the same results as you did.  

I believe this is a bug, but will have to check with @nalind.  If it's not a bug in the code, then the man page needs to be touched up and clarified.

FWIW, when I use 'buildah push' I generally use the full name of the image as you did in your successful push.
